lead_paragraph: We have a few returns from Georgia this morning, chiefly in favor of the Union ticket. In Bibb County, the States' rights candidate is elected by a majority of about 50 votes. Fort Valley Precinct--Houston gives the Union ticket 85 majority. In Marictta, Cobb (Union) has 96 majority for Governor. Rome Precinct.-Floyd gives the Union candidate 63 majority.
